### Generate External Account Authorized User Workforce Credentials (Bash)

Source: https://github.com/googleapis/google-auth-library-nodejs/blob/main/README.md

This command generates an external account authorized user workforce identity configuration using the gcloud CLI. It opens a browser flow for signing in to an external identity provider and stores the configuration at the ADC location, allowing the auth library to use it.

```bash
